description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for suitably an experienced and highly motivated Risk Manager to join the Governance Team within the Corporate Division at Walsall Healthcare NHS Trust.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Working under the direction of the Head of Health, Safety and Risk, and with the opportunity to work autonomously, the postholder will facilitate an efficient and effective risk management system and process across all areas of activity within this integrated Acute and Community provider organisation. The post will be based at Walsall Manor Hospital with the expectation to work or attend meetings across community sites if need arises. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for person with excellent communication and interpersonal skills who will proactively promote improvements and standards of excellence for risk management activities across the organisation. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will be able to work to deadlines, have experience and knowledge of risk management within an NHS organisation and be able to work on major projects with the ability to use your own initiative and judgment when required, and operate effectively as part of a team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Jenna Davies&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Director of Governance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: jenna.davies@walsallhealthcare.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 07795316836&lt;/p&gt;
